subject: College Athletics
Basketball
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Courtney Moses scored 15 points and Brittany Rayburn added 14 to help 13th-ranked Purdue defeat No. 4 Texas A&M, 60-51, on Sunday in West Lafayette, Ind., in the Big 12/Big Ten Challenge.
